                              <title>This is the best time to invest gold ETFs. But what is an ETF?</title>
                              <chapter>                                                   <!--[0-N]-->
                                <paragraph>The ETFs are bought and sold in a stock exchange, like the New York Stock Exchange. They can be traded like a stock and
                                  just like a mutual found, they rack the valutation of an index, commodity or basket of assets instead of a single stock</paragraph>                        <!--[0-N]-->
                                  <paragraph>How are ETFs bought and sold? Anyone can trade stocks on its own. There are online brokers that allow to you to buy some stocks.</paragraph>
                                  <paragraph>If gold perform well, you will look up some ETFs, and decide on which one you can invest, such as those associated with gold.</paragraph>
                                  <paragraph>The stocks are acquired on online bank, from that moment you can monitor the performance every day.</paragraph>
                                  <paragraph>You can choose to invest in companies and have exposure to different aspects of the market as bullion and mining companies.</paragraph>
                                </chapter>
